This article aims to describe the [[phonology]] and [[phonetics]] of central [[Luxembourgish language|Luxembourgish]], which is regarded as the emerging [[standard language|standard]].{{sfnp|Gilles|Trouvain|2013|p=67}}

==Consonants==

The consonant inventory of Luxembourgish is quite similar to that of Standard German.{{sfnp|Gilles|Trouvain|2013|p=67}}

